<div class="contain">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-6">
    <h1>Estimate A Property's Future Growth Story</h1>

    <p>Use this calculator to display the future value of a property based off a hypothetical growth percentage</p>
    <h4>Here's a Few Tips For the Data You Need to Input</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Value of Property:</strong> Use property listing price from realestate.com.au, Domain's homepriceguide, or our other tool Suburb Data to access the median house price.</li>
      <li><strong>Annual Growth Rate:</strong> Use our suburb data tool, our growth rate calculator tool to help provide some context, or just pick a number out of the blue for fun</li>
      <li><strong>Years To Display:</strong> How many results would you like to see displayed?</li>

    </ul>
    <br>

      <form>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="propertyValue">Value of Property </label>
          <input type="number" class="form-control" name="propertyValue" aria-describedby="propertyValue" placeholder="$">
          <small id="propertyHelp" class="form-text text-muted">eg. 550,000</small>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="growthRate">Annual Growth Rate </label>
          <input type="number" step=".1" class="form-control" name="growthRate" placeholder="%">
          <small id="growthRateHelp" class="form-text text-muted">eg. 5.5%</small>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="displayYears">Years to Display</label>
          <input type="number" class="form-control" name="yearsDisplay" aria-describedby="yearsDisplay" placeholder="Years">
          <small id="propertyHelp" class="form-text text-muted">eg. 10</small>
        </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Submit</button>
          </div>

      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
